    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Damján Neszmélyi (Brussels, 11 January
                    1534)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">He does not know if Neszmélyi has forgotten about him,
                            or if he only has a lot of things to do, and that is why he is not
                            writing to him. In any case, it would be good if he did not only write
                            to him when he needed something. He also asks him to let him know what
                            is going on with his abbey because although Pemfflinger is also going to
                            write to him about it, there are some things Neszmélyi can inform him
                            better about.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Ad Daminanum de Nezmel<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1">Damján
                        Neszmélyi was Vice-prefect of Diósgyőr between 1532 and 1534, see <hi
                            rend="smallcap">Bessenyei</hi> 1998, 84.</note><del corresp="Olahus"
                        >vicecapitaneum</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">vicepraefectum
                        arcis</add><placeName>Dyosgyewr</placeName>.<note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.2">Diósgyőr.</note></p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Ita saepe fit, ut dum amici absunt, eorum non recordemur, quod video
                    in me esse verificatum. Nam nescio, an ex oblivione, vel ex multis tuis
                    occupationibus mei es omnino oblitus, nihilque ad me scribis. Optarem, ut non
                    tunc saltem scriberes, cum aliquid tu hic habes rerum, quod <del
                        corresp="Olahus">si</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">sit</add> mea
                    opera expediendum, sed etiam alio tempore. Ut ex tuis litteris veluti veteris
                    mei amici intelligerem rerum mearum statum, plebanatum istum de
                        <placeName>Myskolcz</placeName> ex petitione <persName>Sebastiani
                        Pemflinger</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.3">Sebestyén
                        Pemfflinger.</note> amici mei reliqueram bono illi viro, qui <del
                        corresp="Olahus">nostris</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">nunc</add>
                    in eo <del corresp="Olahus">esset</del> est, ut esset vicarius meus et servitiis
                    divinis primum, deinde meis istic rebus provideret. Abbatiam etiam de
                        <placeName>Thapolcza</placeName> reliqui<note type="critic" xml:id="note.4"
                        >See Ep. 437.<ref>olahus.tei.15340111_1</ref></note> sub protectione eiusdem
                        <persName>Sebastiani</persName>, ut ad proventuum illius administrationem
                    nomine meo aliquem honestum virum ordinaret. Nescio, quid in <del
                        corresp="Olahus">utriusque</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr"
                        >utrisque</add> rebus meis actum sit et agatur, etsi credam etiam ipsum me
                    de his certiorem redditurum, tamen rogo etiam te, qui illorum locorum meliorem
                    tenes notitiam, ut me de his fac certiorem. Et quantum post ipsum
                        <persName>Pemflinger</persName> potes, cura, ne in absentia <del
                        corresp="Olahus">danum</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">damnum</add>
                    patiar. Erit mihi id gratum. Vale. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3"><placeName>Bruxellae</placeName> 11. Ianuarii anno 1534.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
